Title: XSL-FO Parser
Description: This Project hosts numerous styles sheets for converting to and from XSL-FO.
HomeWiki:
Project Description
This Project hosts numerous styles sheets for converting to and from XSL-FO.

Current Supported Formats:

XSL-FO to RTF
  • FO Page Parsing
  • FO Table, Header, Footer, columns, background color
  • bold
  • Italic
  • Underline
  • FO Block
  • FO Inline
  • Text Align
  • ADDED - List Items

XHTML to XSL-FO
  • List Items
  • Tables
  • Headings
  • Some Font settings
  • a few more which is to many to mention

I will publish more examples and progress on http://www.polemus.net
